						<summary>

						<p>On a hero-stone built into the wall of the Parvatappa temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 14th century.</p>						

						<p>This is dated the cyclic year Pramādi. Other details are not given.</p>						

						<p>It records the death of Nāraṁṇa in a fight and refers to the setting up of the memorial for the warrior.</p>						

						</summary>
